<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-blue);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Landscaping &amp; External Works</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Hard Landscaping</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Hard landscaping across London and the South East — paving, paths and patios, steps, ramps, retaining and terraces, self-delivered by our own teams. The surfaces and structures that make a completed building feel finished, built on sub-bases that last and sequenced so the external package never holds up handover.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Hard Landscaping →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Hard Landscaping,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Paving, paths &amp; patios</li><li>Block, flag &amp; resin surfaces</li><li>Steps, ramps &amp; retaining</li><li>Decking &amp; terraces</li><li>Sub-bases &amp; edge restraints</li><li>Falls, levels &amp; setting-out</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>BS 7533 — paving &amp; block surfacing</li><li>BS 8500 — concrete specification</li><li>Building Regs Part M — accessible approach, steps &amp; ramps</li><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>What hard landscaping do you self-deliver?</summary><p>Paving, paths and patios, block, flag and resin surfaces, steps, ramps, retaining and terraces — all installed by our own teams to BS 7533, on sub-bases and edge restraints built to last. One coordinated package, not subcontracted out.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you build the sub-bases and edge restraints too?</summary><p>Yes. The unseen work — excavation, formation, sub-bases and edge restraints — decides whether paving lasts, so we build it as part of the package. Permeable build-ups are detailed where SuDS or drainage demands them.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Are your steps and ramps compliant for accessible approach?</summary><p>Yes. Steps, ramps and level thresholds are set out to meet Building Regs Part M for accessible approach — gradients, going, nosings and handrail tie-ins all detailed before we set out, so the finished access works first time.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Landscaping &amp; External Works</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/">Landscaping &amp; External Works overview</a><a class="sector" hre